Module eu.lilithmonodia.winestock

Package eu.lilithmonodia.winestock.data

package eu.lilithmonodia.winestock.data
The package 'eu.lilithmonodia.winestock.data' contains all the domain model classes necessary for the WineStock application.

These include:

  • Wine: Represents the data and operations related to a single wine item in stock.
  • Assortment: Represents the collection of wines, likely used for organizing or grouping wines together.
  • BottleSize: Enum representing the various possible sizes of wine bottles.
  • Color: Enum representing the different possible colors of wines.
